3 Sonnet agents resolves 38% of SWE-Bench at $0.42/issue. Solo Opus resolves 35% at $1.20/issue. Multi-agent orchestration is cheaper AND better.\"\n\n## Files to modify\n\n- `benchmarks/swe_bench/` (new)\n- `benchmarks/swe_bench/run.py`\n- `benchmarks/swe_bench/results/`\n\n## Completion signal\n\n- SWE-Bench Lite evaluation completes\n- Results show multi-agent advantage\n- Publishable as blog post with methodology\n\n\n<!-- source: 341-swe-bench-evaluation.md -->", "role": "backend", "priority": 1, "scope": "large", "complexity": "medium", "estimated_minutes": 30, "status": "open", "task_type": "standard", "upgrade_details": null, "depends_on": [], "completion_signals": [], "owned_files": [], "assigned_agent": null, "result_summary": null, "cell_id": null, "repo": null, "model": null, "effort": null, "mcp_servers": [], "created_at": 1774723942.7928882, "progress_log": [], "version": 1}]}
